Container free numerical algorithms based on the template metaprogramming approach and test programs

backend                 # level 1 implementation
backend/exblas          # adapted Exblas library
./                      # Level 2 and 4 numerical algorithms
topology                # level 3 Topology and basic Geometry
file/nc_utilities.h     # shortcut to file extension
geometries/geometries.h # shortcut to geometries extension
